          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3" style="color: #1D1D1F; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 600">Admire Your Dam</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #8E8E93; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-weight: 200">
